## 4. Routing Architecture

### Route Structure

```
/insights                              → Redirect to /insights/thread (new thread)
/insights/thread                       → New conversation, Answer tab
/insights/thread/:threadId             → Specific thread, Answer tab
/insights/thread/:threadId/sql         → SQL tab for thread
/insights/thread/:threadId/sql/:sqlId  → SQL tab, auto-scroll to specific SQL
/insights/thread/:threadId/chart       → Chart tab for thread
/insights/thread/:threadId/chart/:chartId → Chart tab, auto-scroll to specific chart
/insights/dashboard                    → Pinned charts dashboard
```

### Router Configuration

```javascript
// src/routes/InsightsRoutes.js
import { Routes, Route, Navigate } from 'react-router-dom';
import InsightsLayout from '../layouts/InsightsLayout/InsightsLayout';
import ThreadView from '../views/ThreadView/ThreadView';
import DashboardView from '../views/DashboardView/DashboardView';

function InsightsRoutes() {
  return (
    <Routes>
      <Route path="/" element={<InsightsLayout />}>
        {/* Default redirect */}
        <Route index element={<Navigate to="thread" replace />} />
        
        {/* Thread routes - tabs handled inside ThreadView */}
        <Route path="thread" element={<ThreadView />} />
        <Route path="thread/:threadId" element={<ThreadView />} />
        <Route path="thread/:threadId/sql" element={<ThreadView />} />
        <Route path="thread/:threadId/sql/:sqlId" element={<ThreadView />} />
        <Route path="thread/:threadId/chart" element={<ThreadView />} />
        <Route path="thread/:threadId/chart/:chartId" element={<ThreadView />} />
        
        {/* Dashboard */}
        <Route path="dashboard" element={<DashboardView />} />
        
        {/* Catch-all */}
        <Route path="*" element={<Navigate to="thread" replace />} />
      </Route>
    </Routes>
  );
}

export default InsightsRoutes;
```

